>> > > > limit, I define (I'm skipping some
>> > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > details
>> > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > here) q={Omega,0,0,Kappa} and
>> > > > solve the constraints, again
>> > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > componentwise,
>> > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > > with this momentum. The subs
